# Apple Website Clone 🍎

A responsive Apple website clone built using HTML and CSS. This project recreates the modern design and layout of Apple's official website to demonstrate front-end development skills and responsive web design.

## 🚀 Features
- Responsive design for different screen sizes
- Apple-inspired modern user interface
- Clean and organized layout
- Navigation bar and product sections
- Mobile-friendly design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3

## 📂 Project Structure
```
Apple-Website/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── images/
└── README.md
```

## 🎯 Purpose
This project was created to improve front-end development skills by replicating the design and user experience of the Apple website.

